771
00:49:31,677 --> 00:49:33,470
- Apa?
- Aku tersenyum karena senang.

772
00:49:33,554 --> 00:49:35,097
Siapa kau mau menghentikanku?

773
00:49:36,473 --> 00:49:38,267
Kenapa tak datang ke tayang perdana film?

774
