00:54:15,043 --> 00:54:16,420
Hati-hati di jalan.

841
00:54:16,503 --> 00:54:18,422
Aku akan mengirimkan alamatnya.

842
00:54:19,923 --> 00:54:20,966
Baik.

843
00:54:21,717 --> 00:54:22,676
Dah.

844
00:54:25,554 --> 00:54:27,222
Betapa egoisnya aku.

845
00:54:28,182 --> 00:54:29,516
Aku akan dihukum karena ini.

846
00:54:57,044 --> 00:54:59,087
